sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant VSCode
    participant EM as ExtensionMain<br>(activate)
    participant Infra as Infrastructure
    participant Core as Core Services
    participant UI as UI/Communication
    participant Cmd as Commands

    VSCode->>EM: activate(context)

    note over EM: Phase 1: Infrastructure
    EM->>Infra: createOutputChannel('FlowRunner')
    EM->>Infra: new FlowRepository(fileSystem, workspaceUri)
    EM->>Infra: new HistoryRepository(fileSystem, workspaceUri)

    note over EM: Phase 2: Core Services
    EM->>Core: new NodeExecutorRegistry()
    EM->>Core: new FlowService(flowRepository)
    EM->>Core: new HistoryService(historyRepository, config)
    EM->>Core: new ExecutionService(flowService,<br>nodeExecutorRegistry, historyService, outputChannel)
    EM->>Core: new DebugService(flowService,<br>nodeExecutorRegistry, historyService)
    EM->>Core: registerBuiltinExecutors(registry, deps)

    note over EM: Phase 3: UI/Communication
    EM->>UI: new FlowTreeProvider(flowService)
    EM->>UI: registerTreeDataProvider('flowrunner.flowList',<br>treeProvider)
    EM->>UI: new FlowEditorManager(extensionUri,<br>brokerFactory)
    note right of UI: brokerFactory = () =><br>new MessageBroker(...)

    note over EM: Phase 4: Commands
    EM->>Cmd: new CommandRegistry(flowService,<br>editorManager, executionService,<br>treeProvider, outputChannel)
    EM->>Cmd: commandRegistry.registerAll()

    note over EM: Phase 5: Notification Handler
    EM->>Core: createNotificationHandler()
    EM->>Core: executionService.onFlowEvent(<br>flowCompleted フィルタ)

    note over EM: Phase 6: FileSystemWatcher
    EM->>VSCode: createFileSystemWatcher(<br>'.flowrunner/*.json')
    EM->>UI: onDidCreate/Change/Delete →<br>flowTreeProvider.refresh()

    note over EM: Phase 7: Disposable 登録
    EM->>VSCode: context.subscriptions.push(<br>outputChannel, commandRegistry,<br>flowEditorManager,<br>notificationDisposable, flowFileWatcher)
